17MaglevCompilationUnit::MaglevCompilationUnit(MaglevCompilationInfo* info,
18 Handle<JSFunction> function)
19 : MaglevCompilationUnit(
20 info, nullptr,
21 MakeRef(info->broker(), info->broker()->CanonicalPersistentHandle(
22 function->shared())),
23 MakeRef(info->broker(), info->broker()->CanonicalPersistentHandle(
24 function->feedback_vector()))) {}
25
26MaglevCompilationUnit::MaglevCompilationUnit(
27 MaglevCompilationInfo* info, const MaglevCompilationUnit* caller,
28 compiler::SharedFunctionInfoRef shared_function_info,
29 compiler::FeedbackVectorRef feedback_vector)
30 : info_(info),
31 caller_(caller),
32 shared_function_info_(shared_function_info),
33 bytecode_(shared_function_info.GetBytecodeArray(broker())),
34 feedback_(feedback_vector),
35 register_count_(bytecode_->register_count()),
36 parameter_count_(bytecode_->parameter_count()),
37 inlining_depth_(caller == nullptr ? 0 : caller->inlining_depth_ + 1) {
38 // Check that the parameter count in the bytecode and in the shared function
39 // info are consistent.
40 SBXCHECK_EQ(
41 bytecode_->parameter_count(),
42 shared_function_info.internal_formal_parameter_count_with_receiver());
43}
44
45MaglevCompilationUnit::MaglevCompilationUnit(
46 MaglevCompilationInfo* info, const MaglevCompilationUnit* caller,
47 int register_count, int parameter_count)
48 : info_(info),
49 caller_(caller),
50 register_count_(register_count),
51 parameter_count_(parameter_count),
52 inlining_depth_(caller == nullptr ? 0 : caller->inlining_depth_ + 1) {}
53
54compiler::JSHeapBroker* MaglevCompilationUnit::broker() const {
55 return info_->broker();
56}
57
58Zone* MaglevCompilationUnit::zone() const { return info_->zone(); }
59
60bool MaglevCompilationUnit::has_graph_labeller() const {
61 return info_->has_graph_labeller();
62}
63
64MaglevGraphLabeller* MaglevCompilationUnit::graph_labeller() const {
65 DCHECK(has_graph_labeller());
66 return info_->graph_labeller();
67}
68
69void MaglevCompilationUnit::RegisterNodeInGraphLabeller(const Node* node) {
70 if (has_graph_labeller()) {
71 graph_labeller()->RegisterNode(node);
72 }
73}
74
75bool MaglevCompilationUnit::is_osr() const {
76 return inlining_depth_ == 0 && info_->toplevel_is_osr();
77}
78
79BytecodeOffset MaglevCompilationUnit::osr_offset() const {
80 return is_osr() ? info_->toplevel_osr_offset() : BytecodeOffset::None();
81}
